[SN]TITLE[SN]
Jim Stevenson: Southport sign Dover Athletic midfielder on loan

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
National League strugglers Southport have signed midfielder Jim Stevenson on loan from Dover Athletic.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 24-year-old has played 27 league matches for the Whites since joining from Aldershot in the summer.
Stevenson could feature in Saturday's trip to Woking - who lie three points and three places above Southport.
He is the third player that Southport have brought in on loan this week, with Kevin Da Veiga Monteiro and Lindon Meikle joining on Wednesday.
The length of Stevenson's loan has not been confirmed by the club.
